task.summary: Created JAR, updated Crypt to remove some debug points, made some slight changes and optimisations
Created JAR, updated Crypt to remove some debug points, made some slight changes and optimisations

Updated JAR, Optimized slightly, Added helper class MinAR, contains useful `static` methods for creation of archives as well as extraction of archives, added FLAGS, used in MinAR class, used in place of boolean arguments such as `COMPRESSED` and `ENCRYPTED`, added default flag sets, which activate a number of flags, can be used through toggleFlags(...)
Updated JAR, JavaDoc includes package-info.java, updated readme to include basic usage section, and created class test.Test to facilitate the readme and commandline usage
Updated JAR, JavaDoc includes package-info.java, updated readme to include basic usage section, and created class test.Test to facilitate the readme and commandline usage
Updated Catch clauses to use minLog

Added Hashing (to secure whether the archive has been damaged or not), Updated Analyzer and Extractor to support hashes. Hashing can be enabled by setting FLAG.HASH, which enabled in `_default_no_enc`, `_default_enc_file` and `_default_enc_str` option(FLAG[] which can be loaded with `toggleFlags(...)`).
